{"title":"配置latex笔记","date":"2018-02-21T13:35:22.000Z","slug":"Latex","updated":"2020-07-18T12:18:39.441Z","content":"<h1 id=\"配置latex\"><a href=\"#配置latex\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置latex\"></a>配置latex</h1><ul>\n<li><p>如果你的英文不好，无法使用英文界面的VScode可以参考这个方式</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/testcs_dn/article/details/75070415\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://blog.csdn.net/testcs_dn/article/details/75070415</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>如果按以上设置后重启VScode无效可以参考这个方式</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/p930318/article/details/80491499\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://blog.csdn.net/p930318/article/details/80491499</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"资源连接\"><a href=\"#资源连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"资源连接\"></a>资源连接</h3><blockquote>\n<p>texlive2018的安装：<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1LUTlXs5nhjI8Fvx5vbbylg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1LUTlXs5nhjI8Fvx5vbbylg</a> 密码：8kks</p>\n<p>vscode：<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/?dv=win64user\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/?dv=win64user</a> </p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5 id=\"1-解压或打开TeXLive2018的安装包\"><a href=\"#1-解压或打开TeXLive2018的安装包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.解压或打开TeXLive2018的安装包\"></a>1.解压或打开TeXLive2018的安装包</h5><ul>\n<li>点击install-tl-advanceded</li>\n<li>可自选安装路径（可安装在D盘），请勾选”修改注册表中的path设置“为是（如下图所示）</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"2-安装VScode\"><a href=\"#2-安装VScode\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装VScode\"></a>2.安装VScode</h5><ul>\n<li>下载安装包安装即可</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"3-安装LaTex-Workshop插件\"><a href=\"#3-安装LaTex-Workshop插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 安装LaTex　Workshop插件\"></a>3. 安装LaTex　Workshop插件</h5><ul>\n<li>在vscode中的扩展管理中搜索“LaTex”，找到的第一个结果就是我们要安装的插件</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"4-自定义配置-为了生成pdf时不出现乱七八糟的文件\"><a href=\"#4-自定义配置-为了生成pdf时不出现乱七八糟的文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.自定义配置(为了生成pdf时不出现乱七八糟的文件)\"></a>4.自定义配置(为了生成pdf时不出现乱七八糟的文件)</h5><ul>\n<li><p>用快捷键</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ctrl+,</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>打开设置界面搜索设置</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>latex-workshop.latex.clean.enabled</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>将其改为true,并添加一个.gz选项如以下所示</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"workbench.iconTheme\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"vs-minimal\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"latex-workshop.latex.clean.enabled\"</span>: <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"latex-workshop.latex.clean.fileTypes\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.aux\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.bbl\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.blg\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.idx\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.ind\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.lof\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.lot\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.out\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.toc\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.acn\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.acr\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.alg\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.glg\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.glo\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.gls\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.ist\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.fls\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.log\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.fdb_latexmk\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"*.gz\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>  同时确认你的tools设置是否和以下一致</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\"latex-workshop.latex.tools\": [</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"name\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"latexmk\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"command\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"latexmk\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"args\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-synctex=1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-interaction=nonstopmode\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-file-line-error\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-pdf\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"%DOC%\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"name\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"pdflatex\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"command\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"pdflatex\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"args\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-synctex=1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-interaction=nonstopmode\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"-file-line-error\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"%DOC%\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"name\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"bibtex\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"command\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"bibtex\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"attr\">\"args\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"string\">\"%DOCFILE%\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  若不一致则在用户设置中复制粘贴以上代码即可</p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p>  <img src=\"http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/pic/item/99e885fdfc039245760755618a94a4c27c1e25d0.jpg\" alt=\"user setting\"></p></div>\n<h5 id=\"5-至此我们的Latex环境已经配置完成\"><a href=\"#5-至此我们的Latex环境已经配置完成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.至此我们的Latex环境已经配置完成\"></a>5.至此我们的Latex环境已经配置完成</h5><p>至此，我们的LaTex+VSCode环境就配置好啦。打开VSCode，编辑你的.tex文件，编辑完成后按’Ctrl+S’保存，插件就会自动建立LaTex项目，在.tex文件所在目录下生成PDF文件。 </p>\n<p>####　P.S.关于中文支持</p>\n<p>想要让LaTex编译器支持中文，必须要在.tex文件的开头加上： </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\\usepackage[UTF8]&#123;ctex&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/Latex/","toc":[{"title":"配置latex","id":"配置latex","index":"1"}]}